The '''Spilgan complex''' was located on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Hollast VII]]. The [[Trandoshan/Legends|Trandoshan]] [[Mercenary/Legends|mercenary]] [[Nakaron]] fought and [[Death/Legends|killed]] the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance]] [[Agent/Legends|agent]] [[Lanish Ran]] within the Spilgan complex.

